    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Printed numerals, letters, or symbols irregularly occurring in the lower margins of some hand-pressed books for the purpose of recording press practice.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
